---
import LandingLayout from '../layouts/LandingLayout.astro';
---

<LandingLayout title="Terms">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-900 mb-12">Terms</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-lg text-gray-600 space-y-12 leading-relaxed">
      
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-900 mb-8">We’ll keep this simple and human.</p>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">What this tool is</h2>
        <p><em>can i have sex today</em> is an informational tool to help you understand your cycle based on the data you enter.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">What this tool is NOT</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
          <li>It is not medical advice</li>
          <li>It is not contraception</li>
          <li>It is not a medical device</li>
          <li>It is not guaranteed to be correct</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4">Human bodies vary. Data can be incomplete or wrong. The app can make mistakes.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Your responsibility</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">You are responsible for the decisions you make using this tool.</p>
        <p>If a decision really matters, don’t rely on this alone.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">No guarantees</h2>
        <p>We do our best to make the app accurate and reliable, but we provide it “as is”, without any guarantees.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Accounts</h2>
        <p>You are responsible for keeping your account secure.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Changes</h2>
        <p>We may change or update the app over time.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="pt-8 border-t border-gray-100 mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">In short</h2>
        <p>Use this as a helpful aid, not as something to blindly trust with important decisions.</p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>
</LandingLayout>